== 評價 ==
電影在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上的新鮮度僅14%，基於網站收集的7篇評論，平均分為2.2/10<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1009518-hercules/ | title=Hercules (1983) | work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | publisher={{link-en|Flixster|Flixster}} | accessdate=2016-01-09 | archive-date=2020-11-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126102900/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1009518-hercules | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 票房 ==
